SEARCH
Package rawDeepLearningClassifier.dataSelector

Interface DLDataFilter

All Known Implementing Classes:
DLPredictionFilter
public interface DLDataFilter
Score a data unit with a deep learning annotation. Note that this could be an external data unit with an annotation e.g. a click, or deep learning detections generated by the deep learning module.
Author:
Jamie Macaulay
